# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES FOR CONTRIBUTORS
# ============================================================================

# SECURITY REMINDER:
# - This tool processes wordlists which often contain sensitive data
# - Use .local.json suffix for configuration files with sensitive data
# - Clear temporary files after testing
# - Be especially careful with test data that might contain real passwords

# DEVELOPMENT:
# - Test with small, safe datasets first
# - Use cargo clean to remove all build artifacts
# - Consider using docker for isolated testing environments
# - Monitor memory usage when processing large files

